data.description: ON ONE ACRE WITH NO HOA! NEWER ROOF!  NEW HVAC ADDED FOR UPSTAIRS!  Country living close to everything! Welcome to 1012 Wooten Drive! This charming 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom house is now available for sale. Situated on a spacious lot of almost an acre, this property offers plenty of room to entertain and enjoy the outdoors.    As you enter the home, you'll be greeted by floor-length windows throughout that flood the space with natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The main level features a master bedroom, perfect for those seeking convenience. The large living room and dining space is ideal for hosting gatherings and creating lasting memories with family and friends.    One of the standout features of this property is the three-car garage, providing ample parking space for multiple vehicles. Additionally, the third garage is extra deep, making it perfect for storing a boat or utilizing as a workshop area.    The huge fenced-in backyard offers a safe and private space for children and pets to play freely. You'll also find an oversized deck overlooking the back yard and mature trees, providing a serene setting for relaxation or entertaining guests.    Other notable features include a new HVAC unit installed for your comfort, abundant storage throughout the home, new fence installed 2 years ago, and a roof that was replaced just three years ago.    Conveniently located with easy access to amenities such as 5 minutes to Lake Allatoona, plenty of shopping nearby and 575 is just minutes away. This property offers the perfect blend of privacy and accessibility. With no HOA fees, you have the freedom to make this house your own.    Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a beautiful home in a desirable location. Schedule your showing today!
